## The Prime Directive

**NEVER generate code without checking specs/ first.**

- Intent and contracts live in `specs/`: `_meta.md`, `functional.md`, `technical.md`, and feature-specific specs under `specs/001-*`.
- Before writing or changing implementation code, read the relevant spec (functional requirements, API contracts, database schema). If the spec is vague or missing, clarify or extend the spec before implementing.
- Ambiguity in specs leads to agent hallucination; keep specs the single source of truth.

