## Traceability

**Explain your plan before writing code.**

- When asked to implement a feature or fix, state which spec(s) and user story (or contract) you are implementing.
- Reference specific sections (e.g. "Implementing A-2 from specs/functional.md and Task schema from specs/technical.md").
- Distinguish between **Skills** (reusable functions/scripts the agent calls, e.g. in `skills/`) and **MCP Servers** (external bridges). Do not conflate them.
- Commit messages and PR descriptions should reference spec artifacts where applicable.

